  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DevCardList
    Class to wrap the different development cards It holds the different types of development cards and how many there are
    GameModel
    The GameModel object holds a bank, which is of type ResourceList, which contains a list of resources to give to players
    Hex
    class to represent a Hex on the board Contains a location, a resource, and the number that goes on that particular hex
    Map
    Class to represent the entire map Contains Hexes, ports, roads, settlemetns, cities, a radius, and a robber
    MessageLine
    Class to wrap messages and their source
    MessageList
    Class to hold all the messages
    Player
    class that holds all the attributes of a player
    Port
    Class to represent the ports on the board
    ResourceList

    TradeOffer
    Class to deal with trading
    TurnTracker
